{"tid":1640732,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[戰世界魚腩盧森堡]  C朗：為國家隊榮譽而戰！","createTime":"2019-10-09T05:41:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T07:13:18.000Z","uid":54373,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"403b0ade1352accc7281c64fafd770edb92c6c38","tid":1640732,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:41:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">盧森堡 - 世界排名87<br />\n已失8球</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nC.朗拿度曬照:<span style=\"color: red;\">為國家隊榮譽而戰</span><br />\n<br />\n  新一輪的國際比賽日已經來臨，C.朗拿度（Cristiano Ronaldo）已經前往國家隊報導，葡萄牙人也曬出了在國家隊集訓的照片，表示能夠代表國家隊出戰總是非常開心的事情。<br />\n<br />\n  C.朗拿度寫到：「回到自己的國家訓練，代表國家隊出戰，見到那麼多朋友總是非常開心的事情。並肩作戰，我們將會再一次為提升葡萄牙國家隊的聲譽而戰。戰鬥吧！」"},{"pid":"d3104e6bd06c3e8cb15b753d172b666950d18c89","tid":1640732,"uid":35930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:44:44.000Z","msg":"管理管到咁點x得"},{"pid":"79dbff5c4a0982570c30a9df1413183bfbacac2d","tid":1640732,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T06:15:32.000Z","msg":"準備刷數據"},{"pid":"2d2f0fa1c7e3e14bc5253f6625568bb6d62db30b","tid":1640732,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:13:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}